  <brief_title>High-definition Transcranial Direct Current Stimulation (HD-tDCS) Verbal Learning</brief_title>
  <official_title>Enhancing Verbal Learning and Memory Using High-Definition Transcranial Direct Current Stimulation (HD-tDCS)</official_title>
